4/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Futureheads-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-futureheads">Futureheads</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了他们在 2005 年<em>NME</em> Awards 巡演期间与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>一起巡演的经历。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-futureheads-noel-gallagher-told-us-we-were-the-weirdest-band-hed-ever-heard-3807115">The Futureheads：“Noel Gallagher 告诉我们，我们是他听过的最奇怪的乐队”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这次巡演是在 2005 年颁奖典礼之前进行的，The Killers、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-futureheads">The Futureheads</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">Kaiser Chiefs</a>在英国各地进行了演出。当时，包括大学在内的场地是乐队演出过的最大的场地。</p><p>在 2005 年的版本之前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/franz-ferdinand">弗兰茨·费迪南德 (Franz Ferdinand)</a>等人在参加巡演后已成为家喻户晓的名字。</p><p> Futureheads 主唱巴里·海德 (Barry Hyde) <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-futureheads-noel-gallagher-told-us-we-were-the-weirdest-band-hed-ever-heard-3807115">最近在接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>回忆了这次巡演的影响，这次巡演为乐队提供了一个关键的平台，他们都取得了辉煌的职业生涯。</p><p> “所有乐队都在一起，有积极的竞争。我们的排名低于头条杀手乐队，他们根据我们的排名而改变了歌单，”海德告诉我们。 “我们在格拉斯哥的表现非常好——以至于杀手乐队决定从《布赖特赛德先生》开始！” </p><figure id="attachment_3809433" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809433" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809433" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/The-Killers-on-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Paul-Underhill_FilmMagic-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809433" class="wp-caption-text">杀手乐队 (The Killers) 参加 2005 年 NME 颁奖典礼。图片来源：Paul Underhill/FilmMagic</figcaption></figure><p> “回想起来，那是英国独立音乐激动人心的时刻，我希望能有一次对二十世纪九十年代积极的怀旧之旅。回望过去，我们都还那么年轻。我们的鼓手只有 16 岁，甚至在我们第一次美国巡演的场地上都没有被合法允许。”</p><p>海德还回忆了 2005 年<em>NME</em>颁奖典礼，这标志着巡演的结束。 “那是二十世纪九十年代的一个艰难的夜晚！我很伤心，因为我在酒吧找到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simon-pegg">西蒙·佩吉</a>，告诉他我有多喜欢他的情景喜剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/spaced-quotes-4660"><em>《Spaced》</em></a> ，但他不太友好，”他说。 “当<em>NME</em>授予我当晚最醉酒人物奖时，我最终赢得了没人想要的奖项！”</p><p> 10 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kaiser-chiefs">Kaiser Chiefs</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kaiser-chiefs-interview-employment-anniversary-20-years-cribs-leeds-3799110">向<em>NME</em>谈到了这次巡演的影响，</a>这次巡演恰逢他们 2005 年首张专辑《Employment》的发行。 “我认为<em>NME</em>巡演的重要性之一就是<em>NME</em>的重要性，”贝斯手 Simon Rix 说道。 “ [2004年]弗朗兹（Franz）的前一年是第一名，然后他们变得非常庞大 - 席卷美国，带着&#39;带我出去&#39;。” </p><figure id="attachment_3809435" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3809435" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3809435" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Kaiser-Chiefs-during-the-2005-NME-Awards-Tour.-CREDIT_-Rowen-Lawrence_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3809435" class="wp-caption-text"> Kaiser酋长在2005年NME颁奖典礼上。图片来源：罗文·劳伦斯/线图</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说：“我们应该非常感谢<em>NME</em> 。即使我们是第一位，但这是使我们迅速发展并将我们带到很多人面前的众多事情之一。第二年，我记得北极在那个法案上，但是每个人都想做第一段，因为它变得像一个幸运的老虎机。每个人都只是想成为第一个。”</p><p>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ricky-wilson">里奇·威尔逊（Ricky Wilson）</a>随后补充说：“我认为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">北极猴</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maximo-park">马克斯·莫尔公园（MaxïmoPark）</a>之前！我喜欢MaxïmoPark，但要看看北极猴变成了什么……这真是令人难以置信。”</p><p>去年，布兰登·弗洛斯（Brandon Flowers）还分享了杀手在巡回赛中遇到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brandon-flowers-on-when-the-killers-first-met-noel-gallagher-on-the-2005-nme-tour-3556314">的时刻</a>。 “我们在布里克斯顿学院（Brixton Academy）玩耍，我们听说诺埃尔（Noel是我的英雄之一，他走进门，我真兴奋。”</p><p>他继续说：“他直接走过我，直接到瓦努奇，那只是，我就像哦，吧，我们最好密切注意绿洲的鼓手在做什么，但是，是的，他马上是他的忠实粉丝。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-futureheads-on-how-they-revved-up-the-killers-on-the-classic-2005-nme-awards-tour-3809407">关于他们如何在2005年经典NME颁奖典礼上改善杀手的未来帖子，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
亚历克斯·沃尔夫（Alex Wolff）与比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）详细介绍了“音乐火花” https://www.nme.com/news/music/alex-wolff-details-musical-spark-with-with-with-billie-eilish-th------------------- Wolff-details susical spark与billie-eilish to-to-to-touring-togetherSam Warner Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:07:19 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3809383 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚历克斯·沃尔夫（Alex Wolff）和比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们真的相信她是她这一代的声音”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alex-wolff-details-musical-spark-with-billie-eilish-that-led-to-touring-together-3809383">Alex Wolff的帖子与Billie Eilish一起详细介绍了“音乐火花”，导致巡回演出的</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚历克斯·沃尔夫（Alex Wolff）和比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Alex-Wolff-and-Billie-Eilish-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>亚历克斯·沃尔夫（Alex Wolff）谈到与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish）</a>形成“音乐火花”，这导致了他们当前的巡回演出。</p><p>与他的兄弟纳特（Nat＆Alex Wolff）一起，这位<em>世袭</em>演员的音乐项目正在艾利什（Eilish）持续的“打我辛苦和软”巡回演出，而三人最近在单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-nat-alex-wolffs-new-single-soft-kissing-hour-with-vocals-from-billie-eilish-3802162">“软接吻时光”</a>中合作。</p><p>沃尔夫（Wolff）在接受<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/alex-wolff-fraternity-movie-the-line-oppenheimer-1236050683/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞记者</em></a>讲话时详细介绍了他和埃里什（Eilish）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉（Coachella）</a>的联系，承认他是否不确定羽毛&#39;歌手的“鸟类鸟”（Birds of the Feather）歌手的粉丝是他们音乐的粉丝。</p><p>他回忆说：“我们只是在奥斯卡派对上见面并打了下来，然后在科切拉（Coachella）有一个周末，我们来回播放歌曲。” “有这种音乐火花熄灭了，这只是直接的联系。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nat＆Alex Wolff-软接吻时光（官方可视化器）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Of_Y5SFJtk0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “然后纳特（沃尔夫）播放了她的新歌&#39;soft Kissing Hour&#39;，她只是说，&#39;哦，我想制作那首歌。&#39;因此，我们很幸运地制作了它并在上面唱歌，这是我们制作的最爱之一。”</p><p>沃尔夫（Wolff）称这是“让她成为朋友并与她一起播放音乐的荣幸”，并补充说：“这是一次千载难逢的机会。我们真的相信她是她这一代的声音。”</p><p>沃尔夫（Wolff）和<em>遗传性</em>外，最近出演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>奥本海默（Oppenheimer）</em></a>和<em>一个安静的地方：第一天</em>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Billie Eilish: BIRDS OF A FEATHER (Live) - SNL" width="696" height="392" src="https://