ttps://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-oasis-reuniting-for-huge-london-and-manchester-shows-3786823">并暗示乐队演奏了一些大曼彻斯特演出</a>，然后才官方进行了正式表演。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-seemingly-teases-oasis-reunion-tour-announcement-date-3786858">最初还取笑了乐队的团聚</a>，他们的英国和爱尔兰的2025巡回演出日期<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">正式确认</a>。</p><p>最近，他取笑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-responds-to-rumours-of-richard-ashcroft-supporting-oasis-on-reunion-tour-3793657">说</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/richard-ashcroft">理查德·阿什克罗夫特（Richard Ashcroft）</a>和演员都可以支持绿洲， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">这两者都</a>再次<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-cast-as-final-support-act-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3806934">成为正式的</a>。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="“我仍然可以召集那个摇滚的脾气”：利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）的胜利卷土重来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/snlgEbG6Z14?start=1&enablejsapi=1#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>回归公告后，四月份发表的评论也重新浮出水面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-oasis-about-to-record-a-new-album-fans-have-some-theories-3788575">他建议Oasis将在11月录制新专辑</a>，并且在Oasis宣布之后，Noel被发现进入录音室，有些人也指出了这位歌手的事实- 唐作者公开宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-says-he-has-scrapped-acoustic-album-and-wants-to-do-a-defiant-rock-record-3613651">他将在今年早些时候取消一张原声专辑，以赞成更“反抗的摇滚唱片”</a> 。</p><p>在其他地方，Edenbridge篝火协会最近根据Ticketmaster <a href="/artists/Oasis">Oasis</a> Fiasco <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-and-oasis-bonfire-effigy-revealed-in-edenbridge-after-dynamic-ticket-pricing-controversy-3808358">烧毁了雕像</a>。</p><p>在传奇乐队的英国和爱尔兰展览的动荡销售中，一些歌迷感到失望地 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">发现门票价格受到了访问付款页面的动态定价政策的影响</a>。</p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticket-sellers-may-have-to-tell-fans-maximum-prices-after-oasis-dynamic-pricing-backlash-says-potential-new-law-3804848">可以在英国引入一项新法律，要求音乐和体育赛事在购买票务开始时告诉球迷最高价格</a>。它遵循英国文化部长<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-condemns-oasis-dynamic-pricing-in-first-address-to-uk-music-industry-3802194">丽莎·南迪（Lisa Nandy）谴责动态定价</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-ticket-sales-culture-secretary-lisa-nandy-calls-for-review-into-dynamic-pricing-and-secondary-ticket-sites-3789694">呼吁对该政策进行审查。</a></p><p>上周，Oasis还宣布，他们将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">取消数千张通过转售网站出售的即将到来的英国2025年聚会之旅的门票</a>。</p><p>同时，绿洲已经<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-when-theyll-be-announcing-details-of-their-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-3809392">确认他们何时将揭示其2025年南美聚会巡回演唱会的细节</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-teases-that-hes-blown-away-by-music-noel-has-written-for-new-oasis-album-3809373">利亚姆·加拉格尔（Liam Gallagher）的帖子嘲笑他被音乐诺埃尔（Noel）为新Oasis专辑写的“吹走”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
